modName: Sword or Sheath Young kid preset
descriptionHtml:
[b]This Preset is officially a Nordic Woman (Barely) with some mods to make it not so much so.


Preset is using the following mods to work properly:[/b]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?]Fair skin complexion[/url]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos[/url]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]Race Menu

[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12951/?]Enhanced Character Edit[/url] (for nose and eyes. [b]DISABLE ENHANCEDCHARACTEREDIT.esp in your mod manager to get race menu's menu to appear and not
ECE [/b])

[b]Preset needs these to look correct:
[/b]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52841/?]Freckle Mania[/url]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71063/?]Face Light 2[/url]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709/?]Skinny UNP Body [/url](Allow Fair Skin to overwite this, so install this first or reinstall Fair Skin)

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/48160/?]Practical Female Armors[/url] for the 'sword or sheath' effect

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]Eyes of Beauty[/url]

[center][/center][b]Installation:

[/b]place the swordorsheath.jslot file into [b]C:\program files (x86)\steam\steamapps\common\Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets[/b]
author: cma1216
